The paper deals with machine learning and risk minimization, which are core topics in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of game theory in developing the proposed algorithm, which is relevant to the subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve image classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the theoretical properties of the proposed algorithm, which is relevant to information theory (cs.IT) and control theory (cs.SY).
